>\uff0c\u5426\u5219\u7528 <span  style='color: blue;'><span class='wikiword'>GetFoo</span>()</span> \u548c <span  style='color: blue;'><span class='wikiword'>SetFoo</span>()</span>\u000a</li><li><a href='#Naming'>\u547d\u540d</a>: \u7528 <span  style='color: blue;'>foo_bar.py</span> \u800c\u4e0d\u662f <span  style='color: blue;'>foo-bar.py</span>\uff0c\u548c<span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'><a style='color: red' class='urllink' href='http://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/' rel='nofollow'>PEP8</a>\u6709\u4e9b\u533a\u522b</span>\u000a</li><li><a href='#Main'>\u7a0b\u5e8f\u5165\u53e3</a>: <span  style='color: blue;'>if __name__ == '__main__':</span>\u000a</li><li><a href='#Conclusion'>\u603b\u7ed3</a>: \u770b\u770b\u4f60\u5468\u56f4\u662f\u4ec0\u4e48\u000a</li></ol><div class='vspace'></div><div class='sectionedit'><a name='sPython.PythonStyleGuide_4'></a><a href='http://www.elias.cn:81/Python/PythonStyleGuide?action=edit&amp;s=4&amp;auto=y&amp;from=Python.PythonStyleGuide'>(Edit Section &#x2193;)</a></div>\u000a<h1  style='margin-top: 0px;'><a name='toc4' id='toc4'></a>2.&ensp; Python \u8bed\u8a00\u65b9\u9762\u7684\u51c6\u5219</h1>\u000a<div class='sectionedit'><a name='sPython.PythonStyleGuide_5'></a><a href='http://www.elias.cn:81/Python/PythonStyleGuide?action=edit&amp;s=5&amp;auto=y&amp;from=Python.PythonStyleGuide'>(Edit Section &#x2193;)</a></div>\u000a<h2  style='margin-top: 0px;'><a name='toc5' id='toc5'></a>2.1&ensp; pychecker <a name='pychecker' id='pychecker'></a></h2>\u000a<p><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u662f\u4ec0\u4e48\uff1a</span> <span  style='color: blue;'>pychecker</span> \u662f\u4ece Python \u6e90\u4ee3\u7801\u4e2d\u627e Bug \u7684\u5de5\u5177\u3002\u7c7b\u4f3c lint \uff0c\u5b83\u5bfb\u627e\u5728 C \u548c C++ \u90a3\u6837\u66f4\u5c11\u52a8\u6001\u5316\u7684\u8bed\u8a00\u4e2d\u901a\u5e38\u7531\u7f16\u8bd1\u5668\u6355\u6349\u7684\u90a3\u4e9b\u95ee\u9898\u3002\u56e0\u4e3a Python \u5929\