u4e3a\u662f false \u7684\u503c\uff01\u000a</li><li>\u5bf9\u5e8f\u5217\uff08strings\u3001 lists\u3001 tuples\uff09\u6765\u8bf4\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u5229\u7528\u7a7a\u5e8f\u5217\u5c31\u662f false \u8fd9\u4e00\u4e8b\u5b9e\uff0c\u4e5f\u5c31\u662f\u8bf4 <span  style='color: blue;'>if not seq:</span> \u6216\u8005 <span  style='color: blue;'>if seq:</span> \u6bd4 <span  style='color: blue;'>if len(seq):</span> \u6216\u8005 <span  style='color: blue;'>if not len(seq):</span> \u8fd9\u79cd\u5f62\u5f0f\u8981\u66f4\u597d\u3002\u000a</li><li>\u6ce8\u610f <span  style='color: blue;'>'0'</span> \uff08\u4e5f\u5373 0 \u5f53\u4f5c\u5b57\u7b26\u4e32\uff09\u4f1a\u88ab\u6c42\u503c\u4e3a true\u3002\u000a</li></ul><div class='vspace'></div><div class='sectionedit'><a name='sPython.PythonStyleGuide_18'></a><a href='http://www.elias.cn:81/Python/PythonStyleGuide?action=edit&amp;s=18&amp;auto=y&amp;from=Python.PythonStyleGuide'>(Edit Section &#x2193;)</a></div>\u000a<h2  style='margin-top: 0px;'><a name='toc18' id='toc18'></a>2.14&ensp; \u5e03\u5c14\u5185\u7f6e\u7c7b\u578b <a name='Boolean_built_in_type' id='Boolean_built_in_type'></a></h2>\u000a<p><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u662f\u4ec0\u4e48\uff1a</span> \u4ece Python 2.3 \u5f00\u59cb\u52a0\u5165\u4e86\u5e03\u5c14\u7c7b\u578b\uff0c\u4e5f\u5373\u52a0\u5165\u4e86\u4e24\u4e2a\u65b0\u7684\u5185\u7f6e\u5e38\u91cf\uff1a<span  style='color: blue;'>True</span> \u548c <span  style='color: blue;'>False</span>\u3002\u000a</p>\u000a<p class='vspace'><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u4f18\u70b9\uff1a</span> \u8fd9\u4f7f\u4ee3\u7801\u66f4\u5bb9\u6613\u9605\u8bfb\u800c\u4e14\u4e0e\u4e4b\u524d\u7248\u672c\u4e2d\u4f7f\u7528\u6574\u6570\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5e03\u5c14\u578b\u7684\u505a\u6cd5\u5411\u540e\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u000a</p>\u000a<p class='vspace'><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u7f3a\u70b9\uff1a</span> \u6ca1\u6709\u3002\u000a</p>\u000a<p class='vspace'><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u51b3\u5b9a\uff1a</span> \u4f7f\u7528\u5e03\u5c14\u578b\u3002\u000a</p>\u000a<div class='vspace'></div><div class='sectionedit'><a name='sPython.PythonStyleGuide_19'></a><a href='http://www.elias.cn:81/Python/PythonStyleGuide?action=edit&amp;s=19&amp;auto=y&amp;from=Python.PythonStyleGuide'>(Edit Section &#x2193;)</a></div>\u000a<h2  style='margin-top: 0px;'><a name='toc19' id='toc19'></a>2.15&ensp; String \u65b9\u6cd5 <a name='String_Methods' id='String_Methods'></a></h2>\u000a<p><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u662f\u4ec0\u4e48\uff1a</span> String \u5bf9\u8c61\u5305\u62ec\u4e00\u4e9b\u4ee5\u524d\u662f <span  style='color: blue;'>string</span> \u6a21\u5757\u4e2d\u7684\u51fd\u6570\u7684\u65b9\u6cd5\u3002\u000a</p>\u000a<p class='vspace'><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u4f18\u70b9\uff1a</span> \u65e0\u9700\u5bfc\u5165 <span  style='color: blue;'>string</span> \u6a21\u5757\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u8fd9\u4e9b\u65b9\u6cd5\u5728\u6807\u51c6 byte \u5b57\u7b26\u4e32\u548c unicode \u5b57\u7b26\u4e32\u4e0a\u90fd\u80fd\u4f7f\u7528\u3002\u000a</p>\u000a<p class='vspace'><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u7f3a\u70b9\uff1a</span> \u6ca1\u6709\u3002\u000a</p>\u000a<p class='vspace'><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>\u51b3\u5b9a\uff1a</span> \u7528\u5427\u3002 <span  style='color: blue;'>string</span> \u6a21\u5757\u5df2\u7ecf\u88ab\u5e9f\u5f03\u4e86\uff0c\u73b0\u5728\u66f4\u63a8\u8350\u4f7f\u7528 String \u65b9\u6cd5\u3002\u000a</p>\u000a<p class='vspace'><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>No:</span> <span  style='color: blue;'>words = string.split(foo, ':')</span>\u000a</p>\u000a<p class='vspace'><span  style='color: red; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold;'>Yes:</span> <span  style='color: blue;'>words = foo.split(':')</span>\u000a</p>\u000a<div class='vspace'></div><div class='secti